You are implementing the Stage 8 Composition Generation panel (`components/stages/Stage8CompositionGen.tsx`) for a video production pipeline editor. This client component manages Remotion component generation, section wrappers, and asset staging manifest.

Requirements
1. Props: `onAdvance: () => void`.
2. Left: component list by section (collapsible). Each component row: name, status badge, [Preview] button (opens PNG still in modal), [↺] per-component regenerate.
3. Section wrappers listed separately below components.
4. [Generate All Compositions] runs `POST /api/pipeline/compositions/run`.
5. Right: asset staging manifest table — columns: filename, expected (✓/✗), present (✓/✗), [Stage Now] button for missing files.
6. [Stage All Missing] button runs `POST /api/pipeline/asset-staging/run`.
7. Error status shows last error message in a tooltip on hover.
8. Log drawer (expandable) shows SSE log for the active job.
9. `'use client'` directive.

Dependencies

