Prompt Dependencies:
- types_TypeScript.prompt — provides shared types
- sse_log_panel_TypeScriptReact.prompt — provides `SseLogPanel`

Instructions
- Load composition list: `GET /api/pipeline/compositions/list`.
- Load staging manifest: `GET /api/pipeline/veo/staging-manifest`.
- Preview modal: `<dialog>` element with `<img src={previewUrl}>`. `previewUrl` is `GET /api/pipeline/compositions/preview?component={name}` which returns a PNG still path.
- Per-component regenerate: `POST /api/pipeline/compositions/run` with `{ components: [name] }`.
- [Stage Now] for single file: `POST /api/pipeline/asset-staging/run` with `{ files: [filename] }`.
- Collapsible sections: same `localStorage` persistence pattern as Stage 6.
- Status badge: same pattern — done/missing/error with color coding.
- Error tooltip: HTML `title` attribute on the error badge.

Deliverable
- `components/stages/Stage8CompositionGen.tsx` — composition generation panel with asset staging management.

Implementation assumptions (explicit)
- Component preview stills are generated on demand via a dedicated preview API endpoint.
- Staging manifest compares `outputs/veo/` files against `remotion/public/` expected files.

Please produce production-ready prompt content that will generate the module consistent with the above.
